cu.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
cu.explanation_en: Changing the remote SCTP control port to 501 will cause F1 control interface connectivity issues, preventing proper routing and signaling, leading to configuration rejection.

du.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
du.explanation_en: Modifying the local N control port to 501 will disrupt F1 control communication, leading to routing failures, connectivity issues, and system faults in the DU.
